

1) When user clicks ‘Sign up’ button he will be able to create
   an account in the online accessories shop.
2) When user clicks ‘login’ he will be able to access his account
   by entering correct username and password combination.
3)  When user clicks ‘Add to Cart’ all the items that he has
   selected for purchasing will be added to cart along with price and
    subtotal.
4) When user clicks ‘Go to Cart’ he will be directed to his cart
   which will display all the items selected along with price, subtotal
   and total.
5)  When user clicks ‘Pay Now’ he will be directed to payment
   page where he can select his mode of pay.
6)  When user clicks ‘Debit’/’Credit’ he will be directed to the
  pages with respective modes of payment.
